snippet.title: Souls of a Feather | Hunt: Showdown
snippet.description:
Souls of a Feather is now available!🪶

This DLC includes:
- Scourge: Morrigan (Hunter)
- Scourge: Midian (Hunter)
- Wing's Wake (Winfield 1893 Slate Riposte)
- Heart's Dowry (LeMat Mark II UpperMat)
- Cagebreaker (Sticky Bomb)

Welcome to the nest👇
